snippet.title: POKEMON DATA - Types in Each Generation (BEST POKEMON)
snippet.description:
In this video I show you the pokemon types in each generation from pokemon data. I hope you enjoy these visualizations I've made, they took me quite a while to make!

The numbers: https://www.kaggle.com/sekarmg/pokemon/data

If you enjoyed this video with pokemon data and the best pokemon please leave a like! 

Sub if you want to be the first for new videos!
